diff --git a/docs/loop-ingress-and-cli.md b/docs/loop-ingress-and-cli.md
index 17aa39e98df031a948c47593bb0ea5b07ce512d7..fe1df807f2a930d1be5c4e400b5593aa81c37bb2
--- a/docs/loop-ingress-and-cli.md
